Biden sucked at his job or was too old, and they applied that frame to ever=
ything else.=E2=80=9D

Put another way: Vibes, baby! Harris has not outlined any specific economic=
 agenda, speaking only in generic terms about
corporate greed, standing with labor unions, protecting Social Security and=
 Obamacare, and fighting for the middle class. She is framing the election =
simply as =E2=80=9Cthe choice about what direction this country will go in=
=E2=80=9D=E2=80=94conveying an agreeable set of center-left values against =
